gh|about-python|/built-in/types/str/format.py||

{ Left, center and right aligning strings

  Strings are left, center and right aligned with the special characters `<`, `^` and `>`:
code {
'{:<10} {:^10} {:>10}'.format('foo', 'bar, 'baz')
code }

}

